        <item>
            <title>《Baldur&#8217;s Gate 3》不會上 Game Pass   開發商：玩家應課金支持好遊戲</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/%e3%80%8abaldurs-gate-3%e3%80%8bno-in-game-pass/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=%25e3%2580%258abaldurs-gate-3%25e3%2580%258bno-in-game-pass</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/%e3%80%8abaldurs-gate-3%e3%80%8bno-in-game-pass/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 11:42:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Baldur's Gate]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1211028</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Xbox Game Pass 收錄不少遊戲，其中不乏新近推出的大作，不過近日開發商 Larian Studios 就正式宣佈旗下遊戲《Baldur&#8217;s Gate 3》將不會登陸 Xbox Game Pass。</p><p>Larian Studios 創辦人 Swen Vincke 日前接受外媒《IGN》採訪，其表示：「從一開始我們就説過，《Baldur&#8217;s Gate 3》不會在 Game Pass 上出現。」Swen Vincke 表示 Larian Studio 製作了一款非常大型且不用玩家額外「課金」（Micro-transction）的遊戲，認為玩家應該支付合理價錢以支持工作室運作。Swen Vincke 又指，《Baldur&#8217;s Gate 3》製作精良，絕對是「一分錢一分貨」。</p><p>《IGN》引述 HowLongToBeat 數據指，要打完《Baldur&#8217;s Gate 3》線劇情最少需要 57 小時，而如果要把支線任務都玩完，就起碼需要 103 小時。倘若玩家是個完美主義者，希望 100% 爆機的話，就需要最少 146 小時。《Baldur&#8217;s Gate 3》遊戲性如此高，因此 Swen Vincke 反對《Baldur&#8217;s Gate 3》登上 Game Pass 也不無道理。</p><p>https://www.ign.com/articles/baldurs-gate-3-isnt-going-to-be-on-game-pass-insists-larian-boss</p><p>https://www.ign.com/articles/baldurs-gate-3-isnt-going-to-be-on-game-pass-insists-larian-boss</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/baldurs-gate-3-isnt-going-to-be-on-game-pass-insists-larian-boss">IGN</a>、<a href="https://howlongtobeat.com/game/68033">How Long to Beat</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/%e3%80%8abaldurs-gate-3%e3%80%8bno-in-game-pass/game-channel/">《Baldur&#8217;s Gate 3》不會上 Game Pass   開發商：玩家應課金支持好遊戲</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
