        </item>
        <item>
            <title>今晨西隧收多人 $8   運輸署：10 點至 11 點用錯舊收費表</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/gary-zhang-xinyu-extra-charged-via-cross-harbour-tunnel/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gary-zhang-xinyu-extra-charged-via-cross-harbour-tunnel</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/gary-zhang-xinyu-extra-charged-via-cross-harbour-tunnel/life-tech/epayment/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 09:53:40 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[hketoll]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[不停車繳費服務]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[易通行]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210980</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div><p>今日（18 日）是三隧分流次階段分時段收費方案實施後首個工作日。香港立法會議員張欣宇稍早時分在 Facebook 發文表示今日駛經西隧時發現系統收錯隧道費。運輸及物流局局長林世雄今晨曾到西隧入口觀察交通情況。據港台引述駕駛人士意見指，隧道口收費顯示牌不夠清晰。林世雄表示收費顯示牌運作正常。運輸署署長李頌恩今日下午會見傳媒，就早上 10 至 11 時西隧分時段收費服務商出錯收多了錢道歉。據李頌恩表示，今日有 4,700 架次車輛受影響，其中 3,400 架已經獲退款，其餘並非經「易通行」繳費。</p></div><div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210998" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/411746306_377440394790655_4429487829150613886_n-694x416.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/411746306_377440394790655_4429487829150613886_n-694x416.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/411746306_377440394790655_4429487829150613886_n-1280x768.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/411746306_377440394790655_4429487829150613886_n-768x461.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/411746306_377440394790655_4429487829150613886_n-1536x921.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/411746306_377440394790655_4429487829150613886_n.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/Gary4HongKong/posts/pfbid02PsjnfVb4SPGD313tm18tTcvxh2hV3YWb9wxZ9NU4kp1seK7etKFMhyJvymyBHsQEl">張欣宇 Gary @ Facebook</a></p><p>張欣宇在個人 Facebook 專頁上表示收到運輸署答覆，確認西隧在今早（18 日） 10 點至 11 點錯誤使用舊版收費表，致使當時通過西隧的車輛被收錯車費。張欣宇指事件涉及人為錯誤，運輸署方面則回應指會儘快安排退款，並與負責操作的承辦商嚴肅檢討操作流程。</p></div><p>明報就事件訪問張欣宇，張欣宇指對「易通行」不停車繳費系統多次出現人為錯誤感失望，建議政府增設懲罰機制。張欣宇表示今早途徑西隧時，隧道口收費牌顯示應繳付 52 元，但「易通行」應用程式收多了 8 元，即合共收取 60 元。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1210999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/411970532_377440411457320_7061397187541941514_n-339x580.jpg" alt="" width="339" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/411970532_377440411457320_7061397187541941514_n-339x580.jpg 339w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/411970532_377440411457320_7061397187541941514_n-526x900.jpg 526w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/411970532_377440411457320_7061397187541941514_n-768x1315.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/411970532_377440411457320_7061397187541941514_n.jpg 785w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 339px" />▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/Gary4HongKong/posts/pfbid02PsjnfVb4SPGD313tm18tTcvxh2hV3YWb9wxZ9NU4kp1seK7etKFMhyJvymyBHsQEl">張欣宇 Gary @ Facebook</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20231218/s00001/1702879580049">明報</a>、<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1732742-20231218.htm">RTHK</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/Gary4HongKong/posts/pfbid02PsjnfVb4SPGD313tm18tTcvxh2hV3YWb9wxZ9NU4kp1seK7etKFMhyJvymyBHsQEl">張欣宇 Gary @ Facebook</a>、<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/1970454/">星島</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/gary-zhang-xinyu-extra-charged-via-cross-harbour-tunnel/life-tech/epayment/">今晨西隧收多人 $8   運輸署：10 點至 11 點用錯舊收費表</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
