        </item>
        <item>
            <title>平價 AirPods 4 或引入主動降噪，再加 Find My 揚聲器預計 2024 年推出</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/airpods-4/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=airpods-4</link>
